description: The Invesco CurrencyShares British Pound Sterling Trust (the "trust") is designed to track the price of the British pound sterling, and trades under the ticker symbol FXB. The British pound sterling is the official currency of the United Kingdom (England, Wales, Scotland and Northern Ireland) and has been the currency of the accounts of the Bank of England since 1694.
name: Invesco CurrencyShares British Pound Sterling Trust
